snippet.title: RoboMiner 2 - Early Preview
snippet.description:
First video of Robo Miner 2 running on a phone (android)

https://www.facebook.com/RoboMiner/

Robo Miner 2 is a sequel to the famous "Robo Miner" Game. It is currently being developed and will be released for Win, Android, iOS (hopefully)

What do you think about that early ingame footage?
